<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Share Your Problems</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        input, textarea {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        input[type="file"] {
            padding: 5px;
        }

        button {
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 3px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #2670b2;
        }

        .view-button {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Share Your Problems</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <form>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Title" required>
            <textarea placeholder="Description" required></textarea>
            <input type="file" accept="image/*, video/*">
            <button type="submit">Submit</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="notes">
        <p>You can <img src="https://www.weareteachers.com/wp-content/uploads/10-19-800x800.jpg" alt="Text" width="40" height="40"> tweet here, <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRUsrAGvkCd_t5475FRx7tgp2g9HzfAsFkjsA&usqp=CAU" alt="Image" width="40" height="40"> upload photos, and <img src="https://mir-s3-cdn-cf.behance.net/projects/404/64fb0d179128007.Y3JvcCwxMzgwLDEwODAsMTAsMA.png" alt="Video" width="40" height="40"> upload videos.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="view-button">
        <a href="authority_problem_page.html">
            <button>View Your Contribution</button>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="view-button">
        <a href="logout.html">
            <button>Logout</button>
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
